ather is a certified management accountant cma and is also a chartered accountant from the institute of chartered accountants in sri lanka where mr mather received his undergraduate ba degree equivalent mr mather received an mba from cornell university new york source spark networks inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view jonathan r mathers full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like jonathan r mather more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in jonathan r mathers network and community follow changes in jonathan r mathers employment and moneyinmotion connect with jonathan r mather through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example jonathan r mather jonathan r mathers connections  sign up now to view jonathan r mathers  connections » albert y liu executive vice president corporate development general counsel corporate secretary and chief compliance officer verifone systems inc manuel j perez de la mesa dir president and chief executive officer pool corporation andrew w code board member pool corporation david s soares former senior vice president and general manager retail business unit netgear inc patrick c lo chairman and chief executive officer netgear inc david budworth chief technology officer spark networks inc michael s egan former chief executive officer spark networks inc dilantha wijesuriya chief operating officer arc document solutions inc james f mcnulty former board member american states water brett a zane former chief financial officer spark networks inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla daniel a dematteo executive chairman gamestop corp david j oconnor president and ceo the madison square garden company × claim your profile coming soon interes