monsothercotton said he was visited by an angel at age  and both wrote and published many workscommon themessome common themes through out their books include religion being good and what happens to sinnersquestionshow many sisters did jonathan havetf both were religioustf both wrote and published workstf cotton was the eldest sontf cotton didnt beleive in godanswerstttffull transcriptmore presentations by quinten huebner piggypiggywwpopular presentationssee more popular or the latest prezisproductcompanycareerssupportcommunitycontactapps english español 한국어  deutsch português français magyar italiano   prezi inc  termsconnect your facebook account to prezi and publish your likes in the future okno thanks